Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.95,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want it to be a crush, then love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.95,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee koi ni natte ai ni natte
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spread my wings
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hane hirogetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take the good things and the bad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee ii koto mo warui koto mo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Add them all together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subete tashite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.83,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divide it by two and live well
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.83,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ni de watte umaku ikite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:21.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to transcend time
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:21.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toki o koetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevadí mi, ak ti budem patriť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravím, že budem tvojím milencom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môžme tú knihu nazvať "Milenci"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Váš vydavateľ mi vravel,\Naby sme sa dohodli na cene
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.23,0:01:56.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a titule pre vašu novú knihu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Eiri\N"Milenec"\NVydavateľstvo Meirin
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, v žiadnom prípade.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne? Myslím,\Nže je to dobrý názov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.98,0:02:09.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otrepané.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki! Yuki! Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.36,0:02:22.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.13,0:02:25.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki! Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, hej, mám úžasné správy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.57,0:02:31.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O chviľu vydáme CD-čko!\NNáš prvý singel. Nie je to super?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakano vraví, že sme to\Ndokázali mimoriadne rýchlo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.74,0:02:35.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, mimochodom, Sakano je náš producent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je Bad Luck fantastický?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravia, že sme veľmi sľubná skupina.\NAle to som už dávno vedel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.11,0:02:42.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stále trváš na tom,\Nže sa ťa to netýka?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikomu nevysvetlíš svoje správanie,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a odmietaš sa vrátiť domov?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.00,0:03:03.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tebe to možno vyhovuje. Ale čo Ayaka?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keď ju chceš odmietnuť,\Npovedz to narovinu...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.44,0:03:11.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak odmietam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.91,0:03:12.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak odmietam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíš tým "tak"?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.04,0:03:13.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíš tým "tak"?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.78,0:03:16.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rozhodli ste sa bez môjho súhlasu\Na dotiahli to až sem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je čo odmietať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je čo odmietať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš, že týmto\Nprístupom to vyriešiš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.42,0:03:20.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš, že týmto\Nprístupom to vyriešiš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki toho veľa nenarozpráva\Na ľudia ho nesprávne pochopia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je skutočne zlatý,\Nale nerád to nikomu ukazuje.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.69,0:03:33.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viem. Keď bol maličký, bol veľmi zlatý.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aj teraz je zlatý!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pochybujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki dokáže spať len na svojom brušku\Na často je veľmi osamelý!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A veľmi neznáša zeler!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kedysi som ho prinútila, aby ho zjedol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rozplakal sa a utiekol z domu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi rád sa stará o tú\Ntučnú mačku na 1. poschodí...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...preto má v ľadničke vždy krabie mäso.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Má veľký strach z tmy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.65,0:03:55.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...musel spávať s rozsvieteným svetlom\Naž do základnej školy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokonca tú mačku pomenoval "Nyanko-taro"!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mňa kedysi volal "Mika-rin".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zima!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otvor dvere, Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa to správa\Nk svojej sestre? Drzáň.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aj tak je Yuki zlatý!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevyzeráš veľmi presvedčivo,\Nkeď ti tečie z nosa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počuj, máš hlad?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:34.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:38.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A vravel, že ma nabudúce\Nzobere so sebou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čakal si dlho?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokázala si vykĺznuť? Dneš máš deadline, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako by som mohla odmietnuť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stretnutie so samotným Aizawom z ASKu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nedáš si?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to výborné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... pani Seguchi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš ma volať Mika.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, dobre, Mika.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to pravda?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím s tým "Mika-rin".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Záleží na tom?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koľko je tomu dní?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si sa nasťahoval k Eirimu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koľko, koľko, um...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,26 dní...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, myslím, že to bude skoro 26 dní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.56,0:05:41.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri dokázal s niekym vydržať\Ncelý mesiac? Šokujúce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem ťa obviňovať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Len...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.07,0:05:57.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslela som, že niekoho\Nlen tak pustí do svojej blízkosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.38,0:06:02.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiriho nenávisť a nedôvera\Nvoči ľuďom je značná.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Má svoje dôvody,\Nprečo sa tak správa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Yuki je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:15.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti. Vidím,\Nže ho máš skutočne rád.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale Shuichi,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,takmer nič o ňom nevieš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, hneváš sa ešte?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Určite hej, prehnal som to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správal som sa bezohľadne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale chcel som sa ospravedlniť,\Ntak som prišiel...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.44,0:06:57.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč mi to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.87,0:06:58.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč mi to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neprechladol si?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nie, nie! Vôbec!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.38,0:07:12.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lebo som hlupák,\Nbola to moja chyba...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som úplne v poriadku!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mika mi vravela,\Nže o tebe nič neviem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nepýtal som sa jej!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.83,0:07:28.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem ťa spoznať sám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem to počuť od teba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie, prečo to Mika povedala?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akoby som mal o niečom dôležitom vedieť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to, Yuki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem o tebe vedieť všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aký to má zmysel?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to predsa normálne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to smutné, ak o tebe nič neviem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.76,0:07:55.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To stačí!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravím ti, aby si počkal, Eiri!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nedotýkaj sa ma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.49,0:08:23.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si so mnou chcel hovoriť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš, že by si mal\Ntrochu myslieť na budúcnosť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z toho chlapca som nervózna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z teba tiež Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Premysli si to.\NUbehlo veľa času.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, Tatchi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.80,0:09:49.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemal si to tak povedať.\NBolo to interview!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.57,0:09:52.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi to fuk!\NNemajú si dovolovať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa opovažujú porovnávať\Nnás s týmito šupákmi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Patríme predsa pod rovnakú spoločnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sme ASK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som, že mi to je jedno!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.47,0:10:15.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,Kaoruko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.44,0:10:24.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem. Už sa na to teším.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je to, tu je to!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela som, že to tu niekde bude!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.35,0:10:34.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No nie! To by bol škandál,\Nkeby sa ukázalo, že to je Yuki Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nemyslíš, že je to\Npre Shinda úžasný partner?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Úžasný, v akom zmysle?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}"Kto je Yuki?!\NBad Luck (Shindo Shuichi)\NExkluzívne vyznanie!!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naša milostná dráma sa skončila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prečo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spravil som niečo, čo ťa naštvalo, Yuki?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aj to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si rozmaznaný, hlučný...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.78,titulky,,0000,0000,0000,,a mizerný v posteli.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.92,0:11:15.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prepáč! Budem sa snažiť a trénovať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aby sa ti to páčilo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.23,0:11:16.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.83,0:11:17.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buď ticho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:21.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poviem ti to narovinu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neznášam ťa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.24,0:11:33.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, čo budem robiť?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.68,0:11:36.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, čo budem robiť?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki ma odmietol...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.78,0:11:43.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opi sa, plač, alebo tancuj. Vyber si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yasu-ki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bože, som opitý!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal ti to priamo do očí,\Ntak ťa to šokovalo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, prekvapuje ma,\Nže to vydržal tak dlho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to trepeš, Hiro?! Ty hnusák!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už som povedal. Vyber si,\Nči chceš plakať, alebo zúriť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.88,0:12:13.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Možno si spravil niečo,\Nčo mu liezlo na nervy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.19,0:12:18.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, vzhľadom na jeho profesiu,\Nmohol mať milión dôvodov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.89,0:12:22.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nič som nespravil!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.83,0:12:24.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už viem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože som sa ho stále pýtal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.43,0:12:32.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lebo ma trápi, keď o ňom nič neviem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som vedieť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto sa Yuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choď domov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A skús sa mu ospravedlniť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.72,0:12:56.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie ste náhodou pán Shindo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boli sme na vašom koncerte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ďakujem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.97,0:13:04.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čože?! Takže ste vážne ten Shindo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No nie! Super!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne je tá osoba,\Ndo ktorej ste zamilovaný, Yuki Eiri?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Eiri? Kde?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto? Živé nakrúcanie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo? Nejaký incident?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je? Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pomóc! Chcú ma zabiť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Za ním! Nenechajte ho utiecť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo tesné!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tadiaľto!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme, teraz máme šancu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prechádzať sa po ulici bez okuliarov,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...je ako prosiť ľudí, aby ťa naháňali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal by si si dávať\Nlepší pozor, Shindo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá rada od tvojho seniora.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto vlastne ste?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.74,0:14:19.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som, tvoj senior!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa z ASKu! Aizawa Tatchi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASK?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.85,0:14:26.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne! Je to Tatchi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.85,0:14:31.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to minulosť. Už ma s tým neotravuj.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš, že to môžeš takto skončiť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.02,0:14:37.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, myslím.\NUž sa ma to netýka.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.36,0:14:39.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám obavy, že...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.03,0:14:39.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Končím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude mu lepšie bezo mňa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netušil som, že si\Ncelkom milý chlapík.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Môj názor na teba sa zmenil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že sme\Nsa zmierili, Shindo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.69,0:15:05.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie je to dobrý pocit,\Nkeď ťa ľudia naháňajú?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.19,0:15:09.59,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byť populárny sa oplatí, nemyslíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj tak,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.03,0:15:18.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,byť populárny znamená,\Nže ťa stále niekto pozoruje.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počúvajú ťa, aj keď mlčíš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pozorujú ťa, aj keď sa skrývaš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tvária sa,\Nže na ničom inom im nezáleží.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to otravné, nemyslíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.35,0:15:31.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A nepríjemné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Máš pocit, že ich\Nuž v živote nechceš vidieť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Eiri ti dal kopačky?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.86,0:15:39.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to dočerta vieš...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte mi to zdržanie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je čas pracovať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.08,0:16:05.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skončíš s Bad Luck,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,inak sa Yukimu Eirimu\Npostaráme o mediálny škandál.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty sviniar, prestaň...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No tak chlapče, hore s tebou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je s tebou? Bolí ťa bruško?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak budeš spolupracovať,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,garantujem ti, že Yukiho\Nreputácia zostane zachovaná.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alebo mu to chceš vrátiť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potopiť ho, lebo ti dal kopačky?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Odmietam.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.79,0:16:48.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi jedno čo spravíš so mnou,\Nale Yuki s tým nemá nič spoločné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dotneš sa ho a prídem\Nsi po teba aj po smrti!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako si želáš,\Ndostaneš čo chceš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Au!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.63,0:17:24.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Shuichi. Čo je?\NOspravedlnil si sa mu?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Príď ma zobrať...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo máš s hlasom? Znie otrasne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kde si teraz?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pred tvojím domom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.11,0:17:40.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, nemôžeš príjsť hore?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.18,0:17:44.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem sa hýbať. Pomôž mi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.03,0:17:59.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám predsa Yukiho rád...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem mu ublížiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo to musí takto dopadnúť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.30,0:18:10.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože som muž? Nemôžem\Nniekoho ľúbiť, lebo som slávny?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je na tom zlé,\Nbyť s niekym, koho mám rád?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.55,0:18:21.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to zlé.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je to tvoja chyba, Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ich kariéra skončila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ich kariéra skončila.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si ho napadol?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je riskantné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nič mi nemôžu,\Npokiaľ mám toto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.81,0:18:45.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to pustím na verejnosť,\Nbude to koniec pre Shinda aj Bad Luck.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Najlepšia skupina v N-G\Nbudeme my, ASK.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je strachom bez seba,\Naby sa niečo nestalo tomu spisovateľovi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.93,0:19:07.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak spomeniem Yukiho meno,\Nten chlapec to neprežije.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravel som ti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.62,0:19:34.82,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa ho opovážite rozplakať kvôli\Nniečomu inému, ako jeho vlastnej hlúposti,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nikdy vám to nezabudnem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.43,0:19:44.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi vás chránil,\Nkeď ho mlátil Aizawa z ASKu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíte si, že sa vás to netýka...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lebo ste sa rozišli?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak potom...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.02,0:20:03.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ste ho neodmietli skôr,\Nnež váš vzťah Shuichi zobral vážne?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skôr, než bude trpieť?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je to vaša zodpovednosť!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.66,0:20:16.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takže som konal neskoro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.01,0:20:29.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa z ASKu, kde ho nájdem?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.99,0:20:46.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst a noisy crowd of people
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.99,0:20:46.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nigiyaka na hitogomi ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.73,0:20:51.06,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The murmured words melt away
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.73,0:20:51.06,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokeru tsubuyaki ga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.44,0:20:55.57,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scattered at my feet
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.44,0:20:55.57,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ashimoto ni chirabatta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.64,0:21:00.20,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are memories that become blurred by it
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.64,0:21:00.20,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,moide nijimaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.64,0:21:06.18,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wander aimlessly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.64,0:21:06.18,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi aruku
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.18,0:21:09.78,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the brilliant lights of the town
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.18,0:21:09.78,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machi no kagayaki wa
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.02,0:21:13.39,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glaring one way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.32,0:21:18.95,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Illuminate me, on the verge of freezing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.32,0:21:18.95,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoesou na boku o terasu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:25.97,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cold time brings dreams from the skies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.00,0:21:25.97,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumetai toki ga yume o furaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.97,0:21:30.64,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they slip through my fingers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.97,0:21:30.64,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kono te no naka o surinukete
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.64,0:21:35.41,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Counting my wishes, when I wake up
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.64,0:21:35.41,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negai kazoe mezameta toki ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.41,0:21:43.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are there in the wavering vision
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.41,0:21:43.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yureru maboroshi ni kimi ga utsuru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.49,0:21:49.08,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A faint silhouette that guides me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.49,0:21:49.08,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boku o michibiku kasuka na shiruetto
